  "detailed_description": "A terrible combination of distorted nationalism and lust for power resulted in a catastrophic experiment that spiraled completely out of control.<br>In this action-adventure RPG that combines exploration with fast-paced combat, the player must search for keys, lives and energy crystals in the remains of the ancient capital, Brasilia, the stage for the battle between survivors and zombies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/c83287612a419ef4167be077947086ad.poster.avif?t=1710624627\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/c83287612a419ef4167be077947086ad.webm?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/c83287612a419ef4167be077947086ad.mp4?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Capital Fire, a game that combines exploration with dynamic combat, the character symbolizes the hope of a future where justice and democracy are reborn from the ashes, even in the shadows of a zombie apocalypse. Estrela is a young defender of democracy, the last line of defense against a threat that goes beyond patriotic zombies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/04a31a663a3a98bb88026dfcef7165a4.poster.avif?t=1710624627\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/04a31a663a3a98bb88026dfcef7165a4.webm?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/04a31a663a3a98bb88026dfcef7165a4.mp4?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>With her red hair, she uses the X power to capture zombies, take emus out of trances, destroy Fake News machines and defeat bosses throughout her adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/e7917bff2905e584e496e29b571a6757.poster.avif?t=1710624627\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/e7917bff2905e584e496e29b571a6757.webm?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/e7917bff2905e584e496e29b571a6757.mp4?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "A terrible combination of distorted nationalism and lust for power resulted in a catastrophic experiment that spiraled completely out of control.<br>In this action-adventure RPG that combines exploration with fast-paced combat, the player must search for keys, lives and energy crystals in the remains of the ancient capital, Brasilia, the stage for the battle between survivors and zombies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/c83287612a419ef4167be077947086ad.poster.avif?t=1710624627\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/c83287612a419ef4167be077947086ad.webm?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/c83287612a419ef4167be077947086ad.mp4?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Capital Fire, a game that combines exploration with dynamic combat, the character symbolizes the hope of a future where justice and democracy are reborn from the ashes, even in the shadows of a zombie apocalypse. Estrela is a young defender of democracy, the last line of defense against a threat that goes beyond patriotic zombies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/04a31a663a3a98bb88026dfcef7165a4.poster.avif?t=1710624627\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/04a31a663a3a98bb88026dfcef7165a4.webm?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/04a31a663a3a98bb88026dfcef7165a4.mp4?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>With her red hair, she uses the X power to capture zombies, take emus out of trances, destroy Fake News machines and defeat bosses throughout her adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/e7917bff2905e584e496e29b571a6757.poster.avif?t=1710624627\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/e7917bff2905e584e496e29b571a6757.webm?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728460/extras/e7917bff2905e584e496e29b571a6757.mp4?t=1710624627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
